leve.name: What Goes Up
leve.description: The engineers at the manufactory are researching an emergency power reserve to keep airships afloat even after the hull has sustained grave damage, an unfortunately common scenario. One of the engineers believes minerals heavily aspected to wind could enhance buoyancy and reduce strain on the engine, and the manufactory requests pinches of lightsand from the Sea of Clouds to use as samples in the prototypes.
leve.client: Temple Knights Second Commander Ser Handeloup
